Measured, not claimed: 82% golden-set exact · 100% fail-closed · 73% on Spider dev.

00:28.000 --> 00:35.000
Three steps: connect your database, ask in plain English, get SQL you can trust.

00:35.000 --> 00:41.000
Readable, editable SQL · auto-charts · conversational follow-ups · multi-engine.

00:41.000 --> 00:48.000
