00:48.000 --> 00:53.000
Schema-grounded, not schema-dumped. Fail-closed. Six providers, always an answer.

00:53.000 --> 00:59.000
Read-only by construction. SQL shown before it runs. Least-privilege connections.

00:59.000 --> 01:04.000
Live and open source — query your data in plain English.
